<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Options
<br />
Keyboard
<br />
Targetting
<br />

<br />
There are 4 target keys you'll want.  I forget what they are called, but they mean:
<br />
Toggle last two targets (I have this on shift-tab)
<br />
Toggle between self and target (I have this on tab)
<br />
Cycle NPC (I have this on v)
<br />
Target nearest NPC (I have this on F8 and q)</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
<br />
