Could someone explain to me what you use these for?
<br />

<br />
I can see toggle last two being useful when you have one or two mezzed and hitting F8 or Cycle nearest is just too much work. <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="icon_razz.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
But I really don’t see a use for the toggle between self and target.  I have almost no spells in use that I have to target myself in a hurry to get cast.  Self-only rune is the only spell that comes to mind that I cast on myself in a rush.
<br />

<br />
I apologize if I come off a little rude, I’m not trying to.  Just would like to know where these come in useful for those that use them.  Thanks.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
